===Proper noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# An open-content [[encyclopedia]], collaboratively developed over the [[Internet]], sponsored by the [[Wikimedia Foundation, Inc.]], and started in [[English]] on January 15, 2001.
#* '''2005:''' [[w:Financial Times|Financial Times]]'', December 14 — "Work in the open-source software community or contribute to '''wikipedias''' on your favourite subjects." 
# (''nonstandard'') A [[wiki]]
#* [[w:Thomas Friedman|Thomas Friedman]] — "Just put it up on the web like a '''Wikipedia''' and let people add to it." 

